:: BEFLIX Recipes [beflix] {"position":"1760,700","size":"480,340"}
# BEFLIX Recipes

One plate plus a verb score per state unit. PRESENT and FUTURE map to verbs; PAST is the established hold. Note the reuse: several units share a plate.

<pre class="legos-data" data-kind="beflix-recipes">SU01 surface_house    plate=surface   establish, openMailbox, enterWindow, revealEgg
SU02 light_darkness    plate=passage   establish, travel, drainbattery        [impl]
SU03 troll_gate        plate=descent   establish, slam, ignite, strike        [impl]
SU04 maze_grating      plate=maze      establish, reshuffle, mark, revealGrate
SU05 cyclops_gate      plate=lair      establish, openEye, speakName, burstWall
SU06 thief_economy     plate=lair      establish, steal, strike, spillHoard
SU07 egg_canary        plate=lair      establish, delegate, windCanary, dropBauble
SU08 temple_hades      plate=temple    establish, ringBell, exorcise, claimSkull
SU09 dam_reservoir     plate=dam       establish, turnBolt, drain, riseTrunk
SU10 river_rainbow     plate=river     establish, travel, dig, thicken
SU11 mine_gas_basket   plate=mine      establish, repelBat, crossGas
SU12 machine_diamond   plate=mine      establish, feedCoal, throwSwitch, compress
SU13 loud_room         plate=passage   establish, double, echoCancel, takeBar
SU14 trophy_endgame    plate=surface   establish, deposit, win

PLATE REUSE
  surface = SU01, SU14
  passage = SU02, SU13
  lair    = SU05, SU06, SU07
  mine    = SU11, SU12
9 plates cover 14 state units. 2 plates implemented (passage, descent).</pre>

